    "created_at": "2014-12-28T06:54:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-12-28T06:54:48Z",
    "body": "To others who find this, the solution is to manually implement Send boilerplate on your type, as shown in the change log above:\n\n```\nunsafe impl<T: Send + Sync> Send for Foo<T> {}\n```\n",
